                <h2 data-uuid="671228e85a8442e993887710e14f33d2"> Document-Based Investigation</h2>
            </div>
            <h3 data-uuid="1515b7e439d14f9eb2e776802331d9fe">Part 2: Write a Compare and Contrast Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="b93765a779664723b8fe0302ada354a9">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="06aeb75551174dc0ba252c4e39709920">The English colonies began with the founding of
                Jamestown in 1607. Despite a difficult
                beginning, the southern colonies flourished. People seeking religious freedom
                started the New England colonies. The middle colonies were known for the
                diversity of people who settled them. Over time the 13 English colonies
                continued to grow despite many challenges.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="5b9c34f442df4824835895988582257f">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="57cac0686eaf48c5b08d59b560eea749">People in the 13 English colonies came from a
                wide range of backgrounds and had different experiences. Write an essay in
                which you compare and contrast the various perspectives of the people who lived
                in the 13 English colonies.</p>
            <p data-uuid="2ff3210df232415d9e1290b316ab090e">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose your essay.<br />
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="module-close-dbi" data-uuid="9cb35df360b040c79abe2761a3175135">
            <ol data-uuid="5cfdbb9fcbd24001ad08328ec31debaa">
                <li data-uuid="09a0d85ad3904bc885dae13ac0928713">
                    Review your notes and sources before you start writing.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="026c6e6b9ef348a8a0d8d1c757991410">
                    Use at least <i>three</i> of the sources in Part 1, and develop the topic
                    with relevant, well-chosen text evidence from the documents.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="57c0593c46664246b2bfaae2d62214c1">
                    Cite specific text evidence from each of the sources in your
                    response.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="fb03763a09194a20b8d2b779b13371a3">
                    Plan your essay so that it includes an introduction, several body&#160;paragraphs,
                    and a concluding paragraph.</li>
                <li data-uuid="64157561923444ccaa7d0d160db0b623">Organize your essay in a clear and logical way that highlights
                    comparisons and contrasts.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="993922cbb4f44acb9b95db7f15f3fa5f">Write a conclusion that sums up your
                    ideas and supports the information you present.<br />
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
